peter voser  wikipedia peter voser from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search peter voser born peter robert voser   august  age  baden switzerland nationality swiss alma mater zurich university of applied sciences occupation businessman years active –present title chairman of abb board member of roche holding ag spouses daniela voser children  peter robert voser born  august  is a swiss businessman he served as the ceo of royal dutch shell plc from july  to december  he started his career at royal dutch shell in  working in a number of finance and business roles in different countries between  and  he served as chief financial officer for abb in  he was appointed shell’s chief financial officer cfo and then ceo in july  in april  he was elected as chairman of abbs board of directors contents  early life  career  personal life  awards  critics  references  external links early lifeedit voser was born in baden switzerland in  from  to  he studied for a business administration degree from zurich university of applied sciences switzerland careeredit in  at age  voser joined shell and held a variety of finance and business roles in switzerland the uk argentina and chile as well as chief financial officer of oil products from  to  voser was cfo and an executive committee member of the asea brown boveri abb group of companies voser is active in a number of international and bilateral organisations including the european round table of industrialists and the business council in  he became a director of catalyst a nonprofit organisation working to build inclusive environments and expand opportunities for women at work in  he joined the board of directors of leading swiss healthcare research company roche on  may  it was announced that voser would retire from the company in the first half of  on  july  ibm selected him as one of the board of directors for the company on  january  voser was appointed to the board of directors of temasek holdings on  april  voser was elected as chairman of the board of directors of abb personal lifeedit voser is married to daniela and has three children since september  he has been serving in the position of the chairman of the st gallen foundation for international studies replacing josef ackermann awardsedit in july  his majesty the sultan of brunei awarded voser the title of dato seri laila jasa in recognition of his services to brunei criticsedit royal dutch shell paid former chief executive peter voser £m in his last years – through share awards and other performancerelated bonuses while the company failed to perform well voser was responsible for the controversial projects of the us oil shale lands the niger delta and the arctic oil exploration referencesedit  httpwwwforbescomprofilepeterrvoser  munzingerde  peter r voser executive proflie and biography bloomberg businessweek retrieved  december    httpwwwtemasekcomsgmediacentrenewsreleasesdetailid  royal dut adrb  royal dutch shell plc  ceo peter voser to retire in   traders retrieved  may    ibm elects two new members to its board of directors marketwatch retrieved  july    forshaw stephen temasek appoints three more board members temasek holdings temasek holdings retrieved  april    peter voser biography at shellcom  international students’ committee changes in the board of trustees retrieved  may   httpwwwtemasekcomsgmediacentrenewsreleasesdetailid  former shell chief paid £m over two years despite profit warning annual report reveals how peter voser made enormous gains through share awards and other performancerelated bonuses the guardian  march  european round table of industrialists  members catalyst boards roche announces change in board of directors peter voser entry on roche board of directors external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to peter voser meet shell’s new ceo fortune magazine interview  jul  delivering energy through innovation  interview  jan  shell ceo keeps foot on accelerator  interview  jun 