ounced that voser would retire from the company in the first half of  on  july  ibm selected him as one of the board of directors for the company on  january  voser was appointed to the board of directors of temasek holdings on  april  voser was elected as chairman of the board of directors of abb personal lifeedit voser is married to daniela and has three children since september  he has been serving in the position of the chairman of the st gallen foundation for international studies replacing josef ackermann awardsedit in july  his majesty the sultan of brunei awarded voser the title of dato seri laila jasa in recognition of his services to brunei criticsedit royal dutch shell paid former chief executive peter voser £m in his last years – through share awards and other performancerelated bonuses while the company failed to perform well voser was responsible for the controversial projects of the us oil shale lands the niger delta and the arctic oil exploration referencesedit  httpwwwforbescomprofilepeterrvoser  munzingerde  peter r voser executive proflie and biography bloomberg businessweek retrieved  december    httpwwwtemasekcomsgmediacentrenewsreleasesdetailid  royal dut adrb  royal dutch shell plc  ceo peter voser to retire in   traders retrieved  may    ibm elects two new members to its board of directors marketwatch retrieved  july    forshaw stephen temasek appoints three more board members temasek holdings temasek holdings retrieved  april    peter voser biography at shellcom  international students’ committee changes in the board of trustees retrieved  may   httpwwwtemasekcomsgmediacentrenewsreleasesdetailid  former shell chief paid £m over two years despite profit warning annual report reveals how peter voser made enormous gains through share awards and other performancerelated bonuses the guardian  march  european round table of industrialists  members catalyst boards roche announces change in board of directors peter voser entry on roche board of directors external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to peter voser meet shell’s new ceo fortune magazine interview  jul  delivering energy through innovation  interview  jan  shell ceo keeps foot on accelerator  interview  jun  i’m open to critics but i have a business to run  interview  may  business positions preceded by jeroen van der veer chief executive officer of royal dutch shell – succeeded by ben van beurden v t e chief executives of royal dutch shell pre managing director general md of royal dutch petroleum   titled md – johannes arnoldus de gelder – jean baptiste august kessler – henri wilhelm august deterding  titled general md – henri wilhelm august deterding – frits de kok chairmen of shell transport  trading – – marcus samuel – walter samuel  to  chairman of the committee of managing directors – guus kessler – barthold theodoor willem van hasselt – john hugo loudon – jan brouwer – david haven barran – gerrit wagner – carmichael charles peter pocock – dirk de bruyne – peter brian baxendell – lodewijk christiaan van wachem – peter fenwick holmes – cor herkströter – mark moodystuart – philip watts – jeroen van der veer  – present chief executives of royal dutch shell – jeroen van der veer – peter voser –present ben van beurden v t e royal dutch shell divisions and subsidiaries current asiatic petroleum company shell australia shell canada shell chemicals shell gas  power ireland shell nigeria shell oil company shell pakistan former mexican eagle petroleum company joint ventures current aera energy albian sands brunei lng motiva enterprises oman lng pearl gtl sakhalin energy former cellana shellmex and bp brands jiffy lube pennzoil quaker state rainx shell vpower people m king hubbert fred meissner gale norton jorma ollila rob routs jeroen van der veer peter voser facilities and places asiatic petroleum building brent spar mars montreal east refinery proposed pittsburgh ethane cracker plant rocky mountain arsenal scotford upgrader shell building 