sers biography chairman abb ltd a global group of power and automation companies committees audit qualifications · global business experience as chairman of abb ltd and former chief executive officer of royal dutch shell plc · affiliation with leading business and public policy associations former member of the european round table of industrialists and a former member of the business council · outside board experience as a director of roche holding limited and temasek mr voser  joined shell in  and held a variety of finance and business roles including chief financial officer of oil products in  he  read more chairman abb ltd a global group of power and automation companies committees audit qualifications · global business experience as chairman of abb ltd and former chief executive officer of royal dutch shell plc · affiliation with leading business and public policy associations former member of the european round table of industrialists and a former member of the business council · outside board experience as a director of roche holding limited and temasek mr voser  joined shell in  and held a variety of finance and business roles including chief financial officer of oil products in  he joined the asea brown boveri abb group of companies as chief financial officer and a member of the abb group executive committee mr voser returned to shell in  becoming a managing director of the shell transport and trading company plc and chief financial officer of the royal dutchshell group he was appointed chief executive officer of royal dutch shell plc in  and held that position until his retirement in late  mr voser was named chairman of abb ltd in  he is chairman of catalyst and a director of roche holding limited and temasek mr voser is also active in a number of international and bilateral organizations source ibm on    sign up for equilar atlas and view peter r vosers full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryl