urope oil products he became cfo of the global oil products business in early  and a member of the oil products executive committee from  until april  peter was a member of the supervisory board of aegon nv he served on the board of directors of ubs ag from april  to april  he was a member of the swiss federal auditor oversight authority from  until december  since march  peter has been chair of the board of directors of catalyst a nonprofit organisation that works to build inclusive environments and expand opportunities for women in business he has served on the catalyst board since april  in march  he was appointed to the board of directors of roche peter was elected to the board of trustees of st gallen foundation for international studies in may  and has taken over as chairman in september  in july  his majesty the sultan of brunei awarded him the title of dato seri laila jasa in recognition of his services to the state of brunei peter is also active in a number of international and bilateral organisations including the european round table of industrialists and the business council a swiss citizen peter was born in  he is married to daniela and they have three children on catalyzing view all catalyzing becoming an authentic leader a toolbox for professionals of color june   by kim c d’abreu catalyzing nearly is not enough june   by meesha rosa related events view all catalyst event marc leaders workshop engaging men as change agents july   catalyst event webinar women in stem august   donate today how can you make a difference to catalyst peter voser quizzes  lists  trending sign up  login feedback peter voser topics  videos  discussion  writeups back to top  revolvy llc mobile terms privacy contact paste image information here × image source save changes × cancel  × × done cancel by proceeding i agree to the revolvy terms of service and privacy policy ok cancel ok cancel × ok cancel × ok cancel × ok cancel × save cancel × ok clear cancel × ok clear cancel pete